      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just about the money though. it's the fact that i've failed at everything i've ever set out to do. i feel like a complete fraud. the \"resources\" and \"counselors\" won't change the reality that i'm a disaster. there's no coming back from this level of failure. i just feel like there's no version of the future where i'm not just a walking embarrassment to everyone who ever believed in me. it just feels like the weight is too much to carry anymore.",
